from steve lamont subject re point within a polygon in article simon crowe writes i am looking for an algorithm to determine if a given point is bound by a >polygon. does anyone have any such code or a reference to book containing
>information on the subject ? see the article "an efficient ray-polygon intersection," p. 390 in
graphics gems (isbn 0-12-286165-5). the second step, intersecting the
polygon, does what you want. there is sample code in the book. spl
